com.att.cso.opendxl.jython.client.interfaces

Interface DxlCallbackInterface


  • public interface DxlCallbackInterface
    Simple callback interface to pass DxlMessage structure to Java processing module from the Python class. The DxlMessage structure contains DXL fields as well as the payload of the message.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.lang.String callbackEvent(DxlMessage message)
      The callback event that will be called when a message is received on the DXL fabric.

    • Method Detail

      • callbackEvent

        The callback event that will be called when a message is received on the DXL fabric.
        Parameters:
        message - DxlMessage object containing the key data about the message and payload
        Returns:
        String containing the payload for a response if necessary
